title: Dom - polish TV series episodes 6-10
description:
A 25 episodes polish TV series about the inhabitants of a building in Warsaw, starting right after the WW2 and spanning for over 20 years.  The series was made in chunks of few episodes every few years, starting in late 1970&#039;s and ending in year 2000, and shows very clearly the changing political times in Poland.  
Its TV-rip and it has hard English subtitles.
